comments: Graham (SAS) disengages from the contact with Oubre Jr. (PHI), but does not dislodge him from his defensive position.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) reaches in and makes slight contact to Graham's (SAS) arm, which does not affect his SQBR.
Branham (SAS) has a forearm extended when contact occurs with Reed (PHI), but the contact is marginal.
After making the pass, Wembanyama (SAS) trips over Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) foot and the contact is incidental.
Reed (PHI) contests the layup attempt and the contact that occurs with Branham's (SAS) arm after the release is marginal.
Wembanyama (SAS) gives a step of distance as he establishes himself in Maxey's (PHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Graham (SAS) steps out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Champagnie (SAS) initiates contact with Maxey's (PHI) arm as he attempts to gather that affects his driving shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) establishes himself in Jones' (SAS) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Maxey (PHI) releases from Champagnie (SAS) during the drive as the contact that occurs is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before the shot attempt.
Champagnie (SAS) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) has his arms extended as the contact with Wembanyama (SAS) is imminent, but Wembanyama slows down and moves around him.
Reed (PHI) grazes the side of Wembanyama's (SAS) body before cleanly deflecting the ball away and the body contact is marginal.
Council IV (PHI) briefly places two hands to Wembanyama's (SAS) body in the post, but the contact is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) legally contests Champagnie's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) establishes himself in Jones' (SAS) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Jones (SAS) gathers the pass on his left foot and takes two steps before releasing the pass.
Branham (SAS) moves alongside Maxey's (PHI) path and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) releases from Champagnie (SAS) at the end of the drive as the contact that occurs is marginal.
Council IV (PHI) makes incidental contact to Wembanyama's (SAS) arm after Wembanyama deflects the loose ball.
Jones (SAS) avoids stepping out of bounds.
Martin (PHI) gathers the pass on his left foot and takes two steps before his shot attempt at the rim.
Batum (PHI) briefly grasps Wembanyama's (SAS) arm as the two players engage and the contact does not affect Wembanyama's FOM.
Graham (SAS) establishes himself in Batum's (PHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Batum (PHI) legally contests Wembanyama's (SAS) post shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that Martin (PHI) is in possession of the rebound with 0.8 seconds remaining, at which point the 76ers signal for a timeout.  The game clock is reset to 00:00.8.
Graham (SAS) places both hands on Council IV's (PHI) body during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Martin (PHI) drifts forwards slightly, but the marginal contact is initiated by Jones (SAS) placing his non-shooting arm against Martin's body.
Wembanyama (SAS) maintains verticality as he defends Council IV (PHI) at the end of the drive, absorbing the incoming contact as Council IV releases the pass.
Batum (PHI) briefly places a forearm against Wembanyama's (SAS) body, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Maxey (PHI) temporarily loses control of the ball and legally continues his dribble upon recovering it.
The shot clock expires while the 76ers are still in possession of the ball.
